title-group.article-title: Analyst Cell Augmentees Provide Key Support to Exercise ULCHI FOCUS LENS

bio.p: Colonel Pete Vanden Bosch, PhD, is the Director of Programs and Analyses at Seventh Air Force, Osan Air Base, Korea. As an analyst, he’s served USAF in a wide range of functionals, including medical research, flying ops, personnel, operational test and evaluation, and logistics. He’s also taught high school and served as a physicist, missileer, budget officer, and director of staff. Pete is a previous MORS Director. In terms of analytical acumen, he’s sometimes been compared to Dr Jerry Diaz — but never favorably.
